{"tid":2415011,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"［藍到黑×笑到痴］沈大屍點名評契媽同老母麵","createTime":"2021-02-20T01:49:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T12:12:58.000Z","uid":191815,"like":49,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"d9b2f6d7447a3bed7a770f65aa50ea06398b70f1","tid":2415011,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T01:49:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pi_F1gy_1-U?t=221\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fpi_F1gy_1-U%3Ft%3D221&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkkBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=436f028d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pi_F1gy_1-U?t=221</a><br />\n片源 2021年2月19日 RF網台直播節目 「錢錢錢打到嚟」<br />\n<br />\n3分40秒 開始提及留言講老母麵<br />\n4分45秒 講移卡臨收市抽上去，開始提連登契媽呀木(Cathie Wood)<br />\n<br />\n講講下就開始將「契媽掃中資」同「2007年港股老散跟四叔倉單入飛」兩單嘢拉埋嚟講<br />\n5分23秒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大屍：「𠵱啲咁嘅局咪一模一樣。喂，大家記唔記得07年呀，香港都出現咗個大嘅股神呀。唔止香港呀，係亞洲股神呀」<br />\n5分44秒  大屍開始反博網民屌佢講Cathie Wood、Tesla、Bitcoin係騙局，大屍稱嗰班網民係打手。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n8分37秒  重提07年「亞洲股神四叔倉單曝光事件」，再燒落Cathie Wood，稱傳媒有心「造神」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10分31秒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大屍：「嗱，咁嗱，即係騙局或者嗱局其實手法不外如是，關鍵在於<strong>第一樣嘢：造神，第二樣嘢就係對直斥其非、淋冷水嘅人就妖魔化</strong>」<br />\n<del>聽到𠵱到小弟都開始懷疑大屍有非常嚴重嘅被迫害妄想症</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n11分48秒 開始提連登同老母麵出咗個post叫「股災啦！！！！！！股災呀！！！！！！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2413751/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2413751/page/1</a><br />\n12分16秒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大屍：「其實有啲嘢呢亦都係一樣嘢嘅，造神論呢唔單止係造股神，亦都要<span class=\"red\">造啲燈神</span>。而利用造咗𠵱個燈神之後，大家係信咗一個咁嘅⋯潛而默化，咁跟住之後呢就導個⋯⋯所<span class=\"blue\">造出嚟燈神，將某些嘢煲大左，跟住就造個市相反，咁就已經好明顯㗎啦</span>」<br />\n講撚到老母麵係大戶造出嚟嘅燈神咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n13分25秒 大屍開始點講大戶同傳媒點冚佢於不義，搞到佢當年淪為燈神。後來唔再聽記者電話同做訪問，冇咗大屍佢𠵱位燈神，所以𠵱家要搵過第二位燈神（老母麵）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即為暗示老母麵係大戶嘅放風人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後面開始講印度點解取代唔到中國做世界工廠呀，澳洲紅酒龍蝦商人點慘，打老婆打到出曬名嘅TVB偽人康年點屌網民用「武漢肺炎」，大屍點屌網民用「支那」兩個字⋯⋯等等藍到黑嘅嘢睇唔睇就由各位巴打決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba9bd5e563f10715e06338d6b87e1ba88f78117","tid":2415011,"uid":232250,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T01:57:27.000Z","msg":"好耐冇睇佢。"},{"pid":"4989c2fd3b8c5c8a7d49a11a20af7b355a2ae2fa","tid":2415011,"uid":81139,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T02:48:03.000Z","msg":"有咩必要睇呢條小丑9up"},{"pid":"c21b0eb07eacbebf7bed062e1571a9f710267ea8","tid":2415011,"uid":173666,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T02:49:26.000Z","msg":"佢隔離條蔡康年屌人講武漢肺炎唔講新冠肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46bd94d902e1b70acaa3d673059906a303e69f99","tid":2415011,"uid":169116,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T02:49:52.000Z","msg":"大屍俾全世界恥笑到開始有精神病了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb312cc12da6848c1b953dedb803467ed567f26","tid":2415011,"uid":156652,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:06:41.000Z","msg":"人地個楂住幾多錢，你個肥師每星期五就等youtube乞食"},{"pid":"09c370523b26b46c5edfe7ed41ddf1d7cdc7b843","tid":2415011,"uid":156652,"like":2,"dislike":0,"